direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **/strat.prioritize**
  NOT YET IMPLEMENTED

  - Prioritize new strategies
  - Against RHAISTRAT backlog
  - Collaborative with PM
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Read Strategies ---

read-strats: |md
  **Read Strategies**

  - `artifacts/strat-tasks/`
  - `strat-review-report.md`
  - New strategies + reviews
  - Frontmatter metadata
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Ask for Scope ---

ask-scope: |md
  **Ask for Scope**

  - PM specifies product area
  - Or infer from components
  - Labels, team, domain
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Pull Comparison Set ---

pull-comparison: |md
  **Pull Comparison Set**

  - JQL query on RHAISTRAT
  - Filter by product area
  - 10-30 comparable items
  - Priority, status, labels
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Present Lists ---

present-lists: |md
  **Present Both Lists**

  - Existing backlog (filtered)
  - New strategies side by side
  - Key, summary, priority
  - Status, labels per item
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Collaborative Ordering ---

ordering: |md
  **Collaborative Ordering**
  LLM + PM

  - Suggest placement
  - Priority reasoning
  - Dependencies, urgency
  - Review feedback context
  - PM makes final call
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Update Jira ---

update-jira: |md
  **Update Jira**

  - Update rank/priority
  - Update labels
  - RHAISTRAT tickets
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Fallback Output ---

fallback: |md
  **Recommendation Doc**

  - Manual grooming guide
  - Ordering rationale
  - For non-Jira fallback
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Document Decisions ---

document: |md
  **Document Decisions**

  - `strat-prioritization.md`
  - Ordering rationale
  - Final placement record
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#999999"
  style.stroke-width: 1
}

# --- External: Jira ---

jira: |md
  **Jira**
  RHAISTRAT
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Flow ---

entry -> read-strats
read-strats -> ask-scope
ask-scope -> pull-comparison

pull-comparison -> present-lists
present-lists -> ordering

ordering -> update-jira: "MCP available"
ordering -> fallback: "no MCP"

update-jira -> document
fallback -> document

# External connections
pull-comparison -> jira: "JQL query" {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
update-jira -> jira: "rank/priority API" {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
